response.overview: Our first attempt at expressing cobra thought patterns in a form that won’t physically damage the neighbor’s house. It was actually created for our pal Crazy Dave (hence the name) and originally meant to be a joke between friends. He enjoyed it mainly because of certain pornographic situations, and also during this time our friend Arthur Jr. was sold to the Hell’s Angels for original plans to an underground city located beneath Mt. Baldy in Chuck Norris Ohio. We think this DVD tape is okay, but prison taught us we could do better….
response.title: Crazy Dave Tape One
